  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798600/extras/6c72fd14f1fe11f36427471d6710d869.avif?t=1719050988\" width=600 height=193 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798600/extras/dbe71f533c22bd1593b7122e33ae6fe8.webp?t=1719050988\" width=600 height=30 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798600/extras/3727d33922cb8703ece97c2c50864c74.avif?t=1719050988\" width=600 height=380 /></span><br>The protagonist, Fan Tong, majored in law in college, but even after a year of graduation, he still couldn't find a job.<br>He wanted to work at his mentor's law firm, but was asked to lose weight and then cross-dress as a test?!<br>The weight loss journey was anything but smooth... Eventually, Fan Tong completely lost confidence.<br>Fortunately, an accident led him to meet a cute and sunny girl named [Bagel].<br>Thus begins a story of weight loss, cross-dressing, and romance!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798600/extras/ebe7d8d3118a4f15ef9a4110cb041777.webp?t=1719050988\" width=600 height=30 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798600/extras/868ec984c665faaaf5d064b0eca07640.avif?t=1719050988\" width=600 height=260 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798600/extras/13cd77c595a10ab14606e1422b4e808f.avif?t=1719050988\" width=600 height=265 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798600/extras/40c2b6c6e93ca1302d482e9192e15ea4.webp?t=1719050988\" width=600 height=30 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798600/extras/78ff1c4944fe1a1019e08d7992f541da.avif?t=1719050988\" width=600 height=224 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Celebrating the 10th anniversary of \"Gaokao Love 100 Days,\" a special short game set in the same universe.</strong><br></li><li><strong>A short Visual Novel with a runtime of 3-5 hours.</strong><br></li><li><strong>Beautiful CGs and adorable chibi-style art.</strong><br></li><li><strong>A light-hearted and heartwarming romance story.</strong><br></li><li><strong>Includes the author's real-life weight loss experience!</strong></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798600/extras/6c72fd14f1fe11f36427471d6710d869.avif?t=1719050988\" width=600 height=193 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798600/extras/dbe71f533c22bd1593b7122e33ae6fe8.webp?t=1719050988\" width=600 height=30 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798600/extras/3727d33922cb8703ece97c2c50864c74.avif?t=1719050988\" width=600 height=380 /></span><br>The protagonist, Fan Tong, majored in law in college, but even after a year of graduation, he still couldn't find a job.<br>He wanted to work at his mentor's law firm, but was asked to lose weight and then cross-dress as a test?!<br>The weight loss journey was anything but smooth... Eventually, Fan Tong completely lost confidence.<br>Fortunately, an accident led him to meet a cute and sunny girl named [Bagel].<br>Thus begins a story of weight loss, cross-dressing, and romance!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798600/extras/ebe7d8d3118a4f15ef9a4110cb041777.webp?t=1719050988\" width=600 height=30 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798600/extras/868ec984c665faaaf5d064b0eca07640.avif?t=1719050988\" width=600 height=260 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798600/extras/13cd77c595a10ab14606e1422b4e808f.avif?t=1719050988\" width=600 height=265 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798600/extras/40c